title: 10 Books for Teenagers! (gnv64)
description:
Here is a collection of 10 books - 5 PDFs and 5 ePUBs which will be of special interest to teenagers!

01. Child Abuse (Straight Talk About...) by Sydney Newton and Julie Gerrits
02. Club Game - The No-Nonsense Guide to Getting Girls in Clubs and Bars
03. How Can Teen Pregancy Be Reduced by Barbara Sheen
04. Insecure in Love - How Anxious Attachment Can Make You Feel Jealous, Needy, and Worried and What You Can Do About It
05. No More Dating Pigs - You Are What You Date by Norah Marler
06. Sarah Fit: Get Skinny Again! - The Right Exercises to Get Back Your Dream Body and the Secrets to Living a Fit Life
07. Surprised by Motherhood - Everything I Never Expected about Being a Mom
08. Teen Ink Love and Relation
09. The Fitness Fun Busy Book - 365 Creative Games & Activities to Keep Your Child Moving and Learning
10. The Official Book of Me - Tips for a Lifestyle of Health, Happiness & Wellness by Marlene Wallach
